{
  "stem": "18102.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the mainstay was the socialist movement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because in Poland, that was beyond merely political.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was also cultural.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The socialist movement, the Bundist socialist movement in Poland, was a movement that proclaimed equality for Jews on every level wherever they lived.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In fact, they rejected Zionism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They rejected Palestine as-- as the end all home for Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They felt very strongly that Jews were entitled to live as Jews anywhere in the world and as citizens of that culture of that country that they lived.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Never mind whether they were religious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Never mind whether they were not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were secular Jews or religious Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were citizens of whatever country, and had the same rights as Jews and didn't have to wait until Palestine to gain those rights.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So it was really a very, very strong oriented Jew-ish movement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the-- yes, they did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Obviously, this movement was had its impact on the politics of Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were marches.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were-- there were debates.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a great deal of political movement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father was elected as a consequence to the city council of Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was one of the few Jews-- and I don't know if whether there were more than two Jewish members of the city council.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Obviously, the mayor was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the councilman were mostly non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father was elected, because of his activities in the Bund, Bundist movement of Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So yes, there was an interaction, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I wasn't even any doubt, notice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I was advised in no uncertain terms by my father who sat me down to explain that there might be a war.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
